# HUD-first load order:
# 1. Util.lua         - shared formatting, theme, and UI helpers
# 2. Store.lua        - SavedVariables init and schema v10 cleanup
# 3. Core_DingTimer   - rolling XP state, snapshot math, and heartbeat
# 4. HUDText.lua      - pure HUD text formatting helpers
# 5. Core_HUD.lua     - floating HUD frame, animation, and visibility
# 6. Core_Events.lua  - XP and money event mutation
# 7. Actions.lua      - popup-facing setting actions and reset behavior
# 8. Commands.lua     - reduced slash command surface plus compatibility shims
# 9. UI_HUDPopup.lua  - compact popup anchored to the HUD or UIParent
# 10. DingTimer.lua   - event wiring and slash command registration
